column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name], # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + # as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, p.obj, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, FROM #x x, #upload u, PhotoTag p WHERE u.up_id = x.up_id and x.objID = p.objID ORDER BY x.up_id
